content:
Pretty straightforward in the end:

  • new unused variable linter
  • upstream of rw? (but caused some regressions in tests: Joe is looking into these today)
  • don't need MathlibExtras anymore

With regards to rw?, I think the issue is changes with which lemmas are blacklisted. Specifically, allowCompletion permits a bunch of lemmas that rw?should not accept. I'm in the process of confirming this, but if that's the only issue then a fix should be complete today.
